lead_paragraph: Rodney Pryor had 26 points and 10 rebounds, and Georgetown withstood a furious second-half rally to hold on for a 65-61 victory over No. 13 Oregon on Monday in the first round of the Maui Invitational.

headline.print_headline: Georgetown Holds Off No. 13 Oregon 66-61 in Maui
